    46‚Üí## Contributing
    48‚ÜímdBook is free and open source. You can find the source code on
    49‚Üí[GitHub](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook) and issues and feature requests can be posted on
    50‚Üíthe [GitHub issue tracker](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/issues). mdBook relies on the community to fix bugs and
    51‚Üíadd features: if you'd like to contribute, please read
    52‚Üíthe [CONTRIBUTING](https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) guide and consider opening
