for_developers/preprocessors.md
     1‚Üí# Preprocessors
     3‚ÜíA *preprocessor* is simply a bit of code which gets run immediately after the
     4‚Üíbook is loaded and before it gets rendered, allowing you to update and mutate
     5‚Üíthe book. Possible use cases are:
     6‚Üí
     7‚Üí- Creating custom helpers like `\{{#include /path/to/file.md}}`
     8‚Üí- Substituting in latex-style expressions (`$$ \frac{1}{3} $$`) with their
     9‚Üí  mathjax equivalents
    10‚Üí
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
