guide/reading.md
     1‚Üí# Reading books
     3‚ÜíThis chapter gives an introduction on how to interact with a book produced by mdBook.
     4‚ÜíThis assumes you are reading an HTML book.
     5‚ÜíThe options and formatting will be different for other output formats such as PDF.
     6‚Üí
     7‚ÜíA book is organized into *chapters*.
     8‚ÜíEach chapter is a separate page.
     9‚ÜíChapters can be nested into a hierarchy of sub-chapters.
    10‚ÜíTypically, each chapter will be organized into a series of *headings* to subdivide a chapter.
    11‚Üí
